title: Match of the Day - S51E06 - 12th September 2015 - 720p x264
description:
SPORT: Match of the Day
On: BBC 1 HD 
Date: Saturday 12th September 2015 
Time: 22:50 to 00:15

Gary Lineker presents highlights of the day's seven Premier League games with guests Alan Shearer and Ian Wright. Games include a clash between rivals Manchester United and Liverpool at Old Trafford. United completed the double over Brendan Rodgers' side last season and have only lost one of their last seven league games at home to Liverpool, but the visitors will be desperate to avenge their 3-0 defeat there in the previous campaign. Meanwhile, Everton take on reigning champions Chelsea at Goodison Park, which played host to a remarkable game between these sides last season - Jose Mourinho's side eventually winning 6-3. Elsewhere, Arsenal host Stoke, Manchester City travel to Crystal Palace and West Brom are home to Southampton. There's a clash of the newly-promoted teams as Norwich face Bournemouth, while Swansea are away to Watford.

The studio experts are Alan Shearer and Ian Wright.

Running sequence:

Everton v Chelsea
Man Utd v Liverpool
Palace v Man City
Arsenal v Stoke
Norwich v Bournemouth
Watford v Swansea
West Brom v Saints
